{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0a415f1ef","title":"中共湖北省委农业办公室转发麻城县万人大会的三个资料","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"49de4a6894","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":13,"articleId":"f0a415f1ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a59ad5b2e1","type":"title","text":"中共湖北省委农业办公室转发麻城县万人大会的三个资料","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"75e1d281fb","type":"paragraph","text":"兹奖麻城县万人大会的三个资料印发给你们一阅。从这三个资料中，可以看出一个公社、一个生产队的政策兑现情况。这对于进一步的彻底地贯彻执行政策是有好处的。希望各地县委办公室都能将这次五级干部会议的资料整理出来，并送省委一份。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"5202817b09","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共湖北省委农业办公室1959年4月13日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"6f0ffb27d8","type":"subtitle","text":"壹、政策兑现情况","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"344bb72c47","type":"subtitle","text":"一、县退还公社：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"5d675b19cf","type":"paragraph","text":"应退现金（包括粮棉油收购款、商业赊销宽、已收回的未到期的农贷款、调用公社物资折价款及赔偿款）273.9万元，已全部兑现。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"0a0ff77265","type":"paragraph","text":"县调用公社拖拉机两部，抽水机五部，动力机十七部，运输工具五十部已全部退还。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"42c2663b4f","type":"paragraph","text":"县属各部门占用民房838间，占用耕地3283亩，压坏禾苗1874亩，尚未处理。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"410c7b4c2d","type":"subtitle","text":"二、公社和管理区退还生产队","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"e999ee769b","type":"paragraph","text":"应退还现金710万元，已退617万元。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"027ad22e3c","type":"paragraph","text":"应退运输工具701部，已退555部。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"c147a5165c","type":"paragraph","text":"应退机械51部，已退38部。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"3b94833f28","type":"paragraph","text":"应退生猪5604头，已退5071头。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"0aca0252b7","type":"paragraph","text":"应退耕牛1383头，已退1106头。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"7fcd1134db","type":"paragraph","text":"应退羊子560头，已退304头。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"719ad43605","type":"paragraph","text":"应退蜜蜂2305箱，已退1954箱。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"82231144cc","type":"paragraph","text":"应退房屋773间，已退139间。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"974259db05","type":"subtitle","text":"三、生产队和小队退还社员的物资","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"3c5087fb06","type":"paragraph","text":"应退家具12538件，已退5834件。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"6fd2c19efb","type":"paragraph","text":"占用社员房屋1772间，已退634间。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"b8b24ea37e","type":"paragraph","text":"拆社员房屋54386间，现已盖起新房很少。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"bbc3d743ae","type":"paragraph","text":"损坏社员东西应赔款29800元，已赔19147元。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"cae3880eb4","type":"subtitle","text":"四、多劳多得","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"768affd368","type":"paragraph","text":"全县原有881个农业社，58年收入开支账目和分配决算都已基本清楚。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f0a415f1ef"},{"id":"314cdc2cdc","type":"paragraph","text":"按多劳多得进行分配，生产队应再分给社员现金8